        "subject": "LU-2456 lnet: Add support for route commands",
        "message": "LU-2456 lnet: Add support for route commands\n\nThis change adds support for the route lnet config\ncommands to the Dynamic LNet Config project.\n\nCommands added: \"lnet route...\" and \"lnet route_list...\"\n\nA different patch will add the \"lnet route_buffers...\"\ncommand.\n\nSigned-off-by: Doug Oucharek <doug.s.oucharek@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ia230b4d0f81f7fc327d07b937063310a4cbb250d\n"
